net.dean.jraw.models

Class OEmbed

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.models.JsonModel
      • net.dean.jraw.models.OEmbed

  • public class OEmbed
extends JsonModel
    Represents media provided by an oEmbed-style JSON object. Documentation in this class is borrowed heavily from the oEmbed website.
